author: Perri Konecky
title: Ashley Graham's Crazy Workout Is a Reminder to Enjoy Dessert
text:
A post shared by A S H L E Y G R A H A M (@theashleygraham) on Mar 10, 2017 at 10:03am PST 
Maybe it's her smoking-hot Sports Illustrated Swimsuit photo shoot , or her ability to disrupt every stereotype associated with being a model , but Ashley Graham has been a serious source of inspiration and our number one girl crush this year. She's frequently posting her impressive workouts on Instagram, but her latest sweat session at New York City's The Dogpound gym has us in awe. 
After confessing to indulging in a sweet treat the night before, Ashley's trainer is making her sweat it out, but from the smile on her face, we bet that cupcake was worth it! She's running up the block with trainer Dawin Pena pulling her back, as Ashley details the "chocolate with white frosting" cupcake and replicates the drool coming down her mouth. OK before we talk about the cupcake, we have to point out that her huge smile and insane strength are applaudable because that workout is no joke. Related: Model Ashley Graham's Intense Workouts Are Not For the Weak 
Dawin also shared a video of their workout on Instagram , giving fans and fitness junkies another source of fitspo, seen below. With sledgehammer tire smashing, slide board lateral exercises, and more beast mode exercises, it's no wonder Ashley's in such incredible shape. Her workout is a sweet reminder that we should enjoy dessert and allow ourselves to indulge in our favorite treats, because it's great fuel for workouts!
